com.tigertext.ttandroid.user

Class UserManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tigertext.ttandroid.user.UserManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TTPubSub.Listener

    public class UserManager
extends java.lang.Object
implements TTPubSub.Listener
    Created by gautamkanwar on 9/24/15.

    This class holds all the stuff related to a user. This class should have user cache, persistence, http calls everything related to a user. Essentially it should be a local user repo.

        public User updateUserSync(java.lang.String userId,
                           java.lang.String orgId)
                    throws TTNetworkException
        Forces the update of a specified user. This is typically not needed if the user is also in the roster since the server will send SSE events for any user changes
        Parameters:

        orgId - The organization id
        Returns:
